Key Features

The model leverages a combination of numeric/ordinal and one-hot encoded features, including:
- Age, T Stage, N Stage, 6th Stage, Differentiate, Grade, Tumor Size, A Stage
- Regional Node Examined, Reginol Node Positive, Estrogen Status, Progesterone Status
- Race and Marital Status one-hot encodings

Feature importance analysis highlights the variables most influential for survival prediction.

